a ini penting?","value":"kenapa-ini-penting","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"output-yang-berguna":{"type":"header","text":"Output yang berguna","value":"output-yang-berguna","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":54,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-domain-research-memaksa-pemahaman-logika-industri-sebelum-solusi\">BMAD domain research memaksa pemahaman logika industri sebelum solusi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-domain-research-memaksa-pemahaman-logika-industri-sebelum-solusi\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Untuk apa BMAD melakukan domain research?</li>\n<li>Kenapa domain research berbeda dari market research?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana outputnya berubah planning dan architecture?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>BMAD domain research bukan hanya tentang istilah industri. Ia adalah proses memaksa tim memahami cara domain itu berpikir, beroperasi, dan membuat keputusan.</p>\n<p>Jika market research menyingkap realitas eksternal, domain research menyingkap logika internal problem space.</p>\n<h2 id=\"fokus-bmad-domain-research\">Fokus BMAD domain research<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fokus-bmad-domain-research\"></a></h2>\n<p>Di sini AI membantu memahami:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>tata bahasa dan istilah domain,</li>\n<li>constraint regulasi dan proses bisnis,</li>\n<li>reward/penalty yang berlaku bagi pelaku domain,</li>\n<li>pola kerja dan ekspektasi yang berbeda dari pengguna domain.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dengan cara ini, BMAD mencegah produk AI terdengar generik. Ia ingin produk mengikuti nalar domain, bukan hanya mengikuti teknologi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kenapa-ini-penting\">Kenapa ini penting?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kenapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Banyak solusi AI gagal karena mereka tidak menghormati fakta domain. Mereka mungkin membangun fitur yang secara teknis logis, tetapi tidak sesuai dengan cara orang bekerja atau aturan di lapangan.</p>\n<p>Domain research bertindak seperti sensor. Ia memberi tahu Anda jika ide Anda akan menabrak kontraint domain sebelum masuk planning.</p>\n<h2 id=\"output-yang-berguna\">Output yang berguna<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#output-yang-berguna\"></a></h2>\n<p>Setelah domain research, Anda seharusnya sudah bisa menjawab:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>apakah asumsi domain kita benar?</li>\n<li>apakah ada constraint yang harus diakomodasi?</li>\n<li>apakah solusi kita memerlukan adaptasi khusus?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dengan begitu, planning dan architecture tidak lagi dibangun di atas generalisasi kosong.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171634\">BMAD market research menangkap realitas eksternal sebelum planning</a> — BMAD market research menangkap realitas eksternal sebelum planning</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">domain-research (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171636\">BMAD technical research memvalidasi feasibility sebelum architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171825\">Simulasi BMAD analysis phase: invoice app untuk freelancer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecora